The paper discusses a reinforcement learning problem with linear function approximation, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use of random projection techniques and eligibility traces is also a common approach in this field. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
